Study group 1 (advanced) curriculum

These are the course materials for our study group 1, which started in June 2015. This group is now advanced enough to take on their own projects. This curriculum page is not being updated regularly anymore and serves mainly archival purpose.

Please also check out the curriculum of our Berlin colleagues: RubyMonstas Berlin curriculum
